overview.en: Etheric element (ET10). With the characteristics of decentralization of block chains, non-tampering of data and distributed books, anyone can directly exchange global mainstream currencies online in a completely decentralized and inexpensive way through the ET10 network connected with Taifang's main network. In the real consumption scenario, ET10 can pay for just needed goods and so on. ET10 aims to create an equity-based licensing ecosystem, through a variety of landing applications to improve the ET10 business ecosystem, the combination of virtual and real. Including, but not limited to, dividends, on-line entertainment, equity matching of quasi-listed companies, etc.
overview.zh: Etheric element（ET10）。运用区块链的去中心化，数据不可篡改，分布式账本等特点，通过与以太坊主网连接的ET10网络，任何人都可以以完全去中心化和廉价的方式在线上直接兑换全球的主流货币，在实体消费场景ET10可以支付生活刚需品等。ET10旨在打造一个股权型通证生态，通过多种落地应用完善ET10商业生态，虚实结合。包括但不限于分红、链上娱乐、准上市公司股权对标等。
